<div data-controller="country-selection">
<%= hidden_field_tag "countries_and_assessments", @selectables.to_json, data: { target: "country-selection.selectables" } %>
<div class="landing container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col left-panel">
      <h1 class="landing-heading my-4">A good heading...</h1>

      <p>
        World Health Organization (WHO) and its partners have developed a tool
        with a list of benchmarks and corresponding actions that can be applied
        to increase the performance of countries in emergency preparedness
        through the development and implementation of a National Action Plan for
        Health Security (NAPHS).
      </p>

      <p>
        Use this tool to get help with creating a draft plan, explore best
        practices in the reference library, or browse the benchmarks.
      </p>

      <%= form_tag '/country_select' do %>
      <div class="input-group">
          <%= select_tag "country",
              options_from_collection_for_select(@countries, 'name', 'name'),
              class: "custom-select",
              data: { target: "country-selection.selectedCountry" } %>
        <div class="input-group-append">
          <%= button_tag "Get Started", type: :button, data: { action:
          "country-selection#select" }, class: "btn text-white bg-green" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="col"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" id="assessment-selection-modal">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title">Let's get started on CountryName.</h1>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="close"
          data-dismiss="modal"
          aria-label="Close"
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>
          Our plans are comprised of activities based off of the gap between the
          capacity score and step up score.
        </p>

        <p>
          You can create a plan from the Joint External Evaluation (JEE) or
          State Party Self-Assessment Annual Reporting (SPAR) scores.
        </p>

        <p>
          If the country hasnâ€™t done either assessment, you can create a plan
          from technical areas.
        </p>

        <p><b>Where would you like to start?</b></p>

        <%= form_tag '/country_select' do %>
            <%= hidden_field_tag "country", nil,
                data: { target: "country-selection.selectedCountryModal" } %>
        <div class="input-group">
          <%= select_tag "assessment_type",
          options_from_collection_for_select([], 'assessment_type',
          'assessment_type'), class: "custom-select", data: { target:
          "country-selection.assessmentTypes" } %>
        </div>
        <%= button_tag "Next", type: :submit, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
